LOCUS       Strep_tag                  8 aa                     UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Strep-tag II — an engineered 8-residue synthetic affinity peptide
            (WSHPQFEK) that binds the biotin pocket of streptavidin / engineered
            streptavidin for mild, single-step affinity purification and
            detection..
