                     /synonym="Strep-tag II peptide"
                     /note="Strep-tag II core affinity peptide, WSHPQFEK (8 aa).
                     Synthetic engineered peptide that binds the biotin-binding
                     pocket of streptavidin and of engineered high-affinity
                     streptavidin (Strep-Tactin) in a 3-10-helical conformation;
                     eluted competitively by desthiobiotin or biotin. Atomic
                     part: the 8 residues are the functional unit and carry no
                     internal functional sub-elements. Verified to 100% identity
                     over all 8 residues against PDB 1RSU chain P (positions
                     3-10)."
